      `list-timers [PATTERN…]` ☰
      `→ Linux/init/systemd/tools/systemctl/is-active[is-active] PATTERN…` ☰
      `is-failed PATTERN…` ☰
      `status [PATTERN…|PID…]]` ☰
      `→ Linux/init/systemd/tools/systemctl/show [PATTERN…|JOB…]` ☰ Show properties of units, jobs or the manager itself. Compare with `set-property`
      `cat PATTERN…` ☰
      `help PATTERN…|PID…` ☰
